      "description": "Available is an investment-grade 2002 BMW M3 (E46) featuring the legendary S54 3.2L naturally aspirated inline-six with individual throttle bodies and dual-VANOS variable valve timing. This specimen is equipped with the desirable 6-speed Getrag manual transmission and a factory M-Variable differential lock. The chassis is structurally perfect; the rear subframe has been proactively reinforced, and the rod bearing service is documented and up to date. This M3 delivers a linear power band and an 8,000 RPM redline with surgical precision. The exterior retains its factory depth and clarity, while the undercarriage remains free of corrosion or fluid seepage. A turn-key collector example for the most discerning enthusiast.",
